descriptionHtml:
Listen to the best of the music and radio broadcast throughout the world with a touch of your finger!

MyRadio is an app made to bring you online radio and music listen on your Android from broadcast stations all over the globe.

Via this app, you can enjoy all forms of free popular radio and music listen anytime and anywhere.

-Easy and convenient to use interface for even first time users.
-Favourite list to save your favourite radio and music stations.
-Sleep timer so you can enjoy the music without having to turn it off yourself.
-Quick search function so you can search for your radio stations in no time.
Note: this mobile application requires an internet connection (3G / 4G / 5G or wifi)

creator: PB Solutions
descriptionHtml:
Radio Azerbaijan + World Radio, 24 hours a day non-stop;
Listen to your favorite music in high quality;
Listen to this music apps, able to runs in the background;
This music app brings you free radio stations from all over the world;
Search by song name, country, genre to easily find a station;
Add an online radio to your favourites list;
View an online radio in your recent list;
Listen through the smartphone's loudspeakers or via Bluetooth;
Set a sleep timer to turn the app off automatically;
Personalize your phone with selection themes;
Share with friends via Social Media, SMS or Email.


Note:
This Radio app requires an internet connection, 3G/4G/5G or Wi-Fi network in order to tune in radio stations. Some FM radio stations may not work/fail to play because their stream is temporarily offline.

Disclaimer :
This is an unofficial apps. This apps and its content are not officially endorsed or produced by, nor associated with or affiliated with the music artist(s) or any associated entities of the artist(s), such as management or record label.

This application is limited to entertaining fans of old songs, while song labels, artist labels and record labels are wholly owned by related companies.

All trademarks and copyrights are property of their respective owners. This application has ads that comply with Google Play Policy and Please support the artists and their companies.
